<gitmoji> <type>: <imperative subject>

# Optional body: explain why, constraints, or migration notes.
# Optional issue reference: Refs #123
#
# Types:
# feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, build, ci, chore, revert
#
# Common gitmojis:
# ✨ feat      New feature
# 🐛 fix       Bug fix
# 📝 docs      Documentation
# 🎨 style     Formatting or code style
# ♻️ refactor  Internal restructure without behavior change
# ⚡ perf      Performance improvement
# ✅ test      Tests
# 🔧 build     Build system or tooling
# 🚀 ci        Automation and delivery
# 📦 chore     Dependencies or repository maintenance
# 🔒 fix       Security fix
# 🗑️ chore     Remove code or files
# 🔖 chore     Release version and tag
# ⏪ revert    Revert a previous change
#
# Examples:
# ✨ feat: add subject regex filters
# 🐛 fix: preserve encoded verification links
# 📝 docs: document Cypress usage
# 🔖 chore: release v0.2.0
